# BHH - A Library for You

## Version: 0.5.0

### Changes in this version:

Commands were modularized.

File handling capabilities have been added.

The ability to reverse text has been removed.

## Developer: Aria
[PyPI Page](https://pypi.org/user/ariakm1394/)

